$(document).ready(function(){$("#addsite").click(function(){var a=$("#sname").val(),b=$("#sdomain").val(),c=$("#sbrief").val(),d=$("#spic").val(),e={sname:a,sbrief:c,sdomain:b,spic:d};$.ajax({data:e,url:"/addsite",dataType:"json",cache:!1,timeout:5e3,type:"get",success:function(a){$("#spanMessage").html(0===a.status?"Site增加成功":"Site增加失败")},error:function(){$("#spanMessage").html("ERROR")}})}),$("#updatesite").click(function(){var a=$("#snname").val(),b=$("#sndomain").val(),c=$("#snbrief").val(),d=$("#snpic").val(),e={snname:a,snbrief:c,sndomain:b,snpic:d};$.ajax({data:e,url:"/updatesite",dataType:"json",cache:!1,timeout:5e3,type:"get",success:function(a){$("#spanMessage2").html(0===a.status?"Site编辑成功":"Site编辑失败")},error:function(){$("#spanMessage2").html("ERROR")}})}),$("#sndomain").blur(function(){var a=$("#snname"),b=$("#sndomain"),c=$("#snbrief"),d=$("#snpic"),e=b.val(),f={domainname:e};$.ajax({data:f,url:"/getsite",dataType:"json",cache:!1,timeout:5e3,type:"get",success:function(b){0===b.status?(a.val(b.site.sname),c.val(b.site.sbrief),d.val(b.site.spic)):($("#spanMessage2").html("Site查找失败"),a.val(""),c.val(""),d.val(""))},error:function(){$("#spanMessage2").html("ERROR")}})})});